---
import PageContainer from "../components/PageContainer.astro";
import PageHeader from "../components/PageHeader.astro";
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Contact — hmziq.rs" description="How to get in touch with hmziq.rs.">
  <PageContainer>
    <PageHeader
      title="Contact"
      description="A basic contact page for questions, corrections, sponsorships, and site-related inquiries."
      class="mb-8"
    />

    <section class="grid gap-4 max-w-3xl">
      <article class="rounded-[1.25rem] border border-base-300 bg-base-200/55 p-5 sm:p-6">
        <p class="mb-3 font-mono text-[0.72rem] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-base-content/52">
          Status
        </p>
        <p class="text-base leading-7 text-base-content/78">
          A direct public contact address is not published on the site yet. This page exists as the
          canonical place for contact details and inquiry guidance as they are added.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-[1.25rem] border border-base-300 bg-base-100/70 p-5 sm:p-6">
        <p class="mb-3 font-mono text-[0.72rem] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-base-content/52">
          General
        </p>
        <p class="text-base leading-7 text-base-content/78">
          Use this page for general questions about posts, technical corrections, broken links, or
          requests related to published material.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-[1.25rem] border border-base-300 bg-base-100/70 p-5 sm:p-6">
        <p class="mb-3 font-mono text-[0.72rem] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-base-content/52">
          Sponsorships
        </p>
        <p class="text-base leading-7 text-base-content/78">
          Static advertising, sponsorships, and related commercial inquiries should be routed through
          the contact details that will be listed here when they are made public.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-[1.25rem] border border-base-300 bg-base-100/70 p-5 sm:p-6">
        <p class="mb-3 font-mono text-[0.72rem] uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-base-content/52">
          Note
        </p>
        <p class="text-base leading-7 text-base-content/78">
          Once a public email address or preferred contact channel is available, this page should be
          updated so the site has a clear single source of truth.
        </p>
      </article>
    </section>
  </PageContainer>
</BaseLayout>
